title: A Woman Calls in to Talk about Being the Mistress in an Affair
description: Last week, Dave brought up how surprised he was to find out so many people that are cheating and a listener emailed us because she wanted to tell her side of the story, being the mistress in an affair.  People do NOT like her but she still shares her story.
